Aim

To interface LCD and display characters.

Theory
LCD displays characters
RS selects command/data
RW selects read/write
EN enables operation
Data sent via port
Requires initialization
Used in display systems
Simulator Used

EdSim51

Code
ORG 0000H
MOV A, #'A'
MOV P2, A
SJMP $
END
Observation
Character ‘A’ displayed
LCD responded correctly
Output verified
Conclusion

Thus, LCD interfacing and display operation were successful.
